    "The grounding is all in the T3 module, and can only be conferred by the GPT/LLM module's words to describe and name new categories (IVG) if it uses the names of features that are already grounded (directly or indirectly) in the T3 module.",
    "The transaction is unidirectional; there is no bidirectional integration of grounded bottom-up categories and ungrounded topdown categories.",
